rows.label: tlk41700122_06_msg0001
rows.name:
A bunch of refugees from Acedia have
wound up in Trigo, but never fear.
Kloom Farm can provide for them all!

rows.label: tlk41700122_06_msg0002
rows.name:
Be it a hundred people or a thousand,
we'll feed 'em all on our tasty veg!

rows.label: tlk41700122_06_msg0003
rows.name:
Each one of our vegetables is packed
to bursting with nutrients, so there's
no chance they'll go hungry.

rows.label: tlk41700122_06_msg0004
rows.name:
Hahaha! This is all thanks to the
hard work my family's put in over
the generations.
